  <li>I'm another item</li>
</ul>
Play

An ordered list	<ol>	
html

Copy
Play
<ol>
  <li>I'm the first item</li>
  <li>I'm the second item</li>
</ol>
Play

A definition list	<dl>	
html

Copy
Play
<dl>
  <dt>A Term</dt>
  <dd>Definition of a term</dd>
  <dt>Another Term</dt>
  <dd>Definition of another term</dd>
</dl>
Play

A horizontal rule	<hr>	
